'''《公告牌》数字歌曲榜'''（{{lang-en|Digital Songs}}），前称'''热门数字歌曲榜'''（{{lang|en|Hot Digital Songs}}），<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5862620/pitbull-kesha-take-timber-to-top-of-hot-100|work=Billboard|title=Pitbull, Ke$ha Take 'Timber' to Top of Hot 100|first=Gary|last=Trust|date=2014-01-08|accessdate=2014-01-09|archive-date=2014-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140126054802/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5862620/pitbull-kesha-take-timber-to-top-of-hot-100|dead-url=no}}</ref>是《[[告示牌_(雜誌)|告示牌]]》根据歌曲全部版本的数字下载量发布的一份音乐周榜单。该榜单于2005年1月22日首次发布。<ref>{{cite journal|date=2005-01-22|title=New Mix for Digital Rankings|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=dRQEAAAAMBAJ&printsec=frontcover&rview=1&source=gbs_ge_summary_r&cad=0#v=onepage&q&f=false|journal=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]]|page=6|volume=117|issue=4|accessdate=2013-03-22|archive-date=2020-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200808090212/https://books.google.com/books?id=dRQEAAAAMBAJ&printsec=frontcover&rview=1&source=gbs_ge_summary_r&cad=0#v=onepage&q&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>由于实体唱片的衰落和数字唱片市场的急剧增大，<ref>{{cite web |title=Billboard updated album charts |publisher=''Billboard'' |url=http://www.billboard.com/bbcom/charts/chart_display.jsp?g=Singles&f=Hot+Digital+Tracks&page=2 |accessdate=2008-06-02 |archive-date=2012-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120929073128/http://www.billboard.com/bbcom/charts/chart_display.jsp?g=Singles&f=Hot+Digital+Tracks&page=2 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
自2004年10月开始，歌曲的数字销售已被纳入许多《告示牌》音乐榜单。<ref>{{cite news|first=Paul|last=Grein|title=Week Ending March 17, 2013. Songs: The Great Chart Robbery Of 2013|url=http://music.yahoo.com/blogs/chart-watch/week-ending-march-17-2013-songs-great-chart-220437064.html|work=Yahoo!|publisher=Yahoo!|date=2013-03-20|accessdate=2013-03-21|archive-date=2013-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131021175856/http://music.yahoo.com/blogs/chart-watch/week-ending-march-17-2013-songs-great-chart-220437064.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

